question: Guáⁿ chiah dataset sī ti̍t-tsiap teh huān-tòe tiong-iong gîn-hâng teh sú-iōng ê gí-giân lâi liáu-kái chu-kim chè-tōe tùi kim-chè chhī-tiûⁿ ê éng-hióng, koh ū siáng só͘ hoat-piáu?
Ake chiah-choā chu-liāu-khò͘ chhut-pán tī 2020 niâⁿ āu, koh chin chheng-chhò͘ kóng sī jîn-lūi chhiú-siá, he̍k-chiá sī chhu-ka-jîn phòe-choá ê?
Tùi chhut-pán nî-tāi lâi kóng, ê-tāi chū 2010 nî-tāi chho͘-kî kàu 2020 nî-tāi, chiah-ê kim-iông chu-liāu-kio̍k ê tùi-siōng ê ián-piàn cháiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Chiah-ê chu-liāu-kio̍k sī chiap-sòa 2010 nî-tāi chho͘-kî ê ki-pún ê chêng-sū hoat-sit (sentiment analysis), ián-piàn kàu 2020 nî-tāi koh khah lo̍k-chi̍p kap choan-bîn ê jīm-bū. Chho͘-kî ê chu-goân, chhin-chhiūⁿ SentiWordNet (2010) kap Financial Phrase Bank (2014), sī leh kā choân-thêng ê jī/chù-gí ê chêng-sū. Tùi phian-piān lâi kóng, 2020 nî-tāi ê chu-goân, chhin-chhiūⁿ SEntFiN 1.0 (tùi tāi-chè-thé ê chêng-sū bîn-chām), REFinD (koan-hē hun-sek), kap FINQA (chhim-tō͘ luî-chhat), chham-ú koh khah hì-mî kap lo̍k-chi̍p ê NLP būn-tê, chiah piáu-bī tio̍h chāi teh tì-sū kim-iông bûn-jī ê liáu-kái tī kim-iông bûn-jī hong-bīn ū hiah-ê tiâu-chéng (nuanced).

question: Tī chit-ê lia̍t-chhut ê chu-goân tang-tiong, ū kúi-ê chú-iàu tùi sentiment analysis (hō͘-iáⁿ chpositive, negative, iā-sī neutral ê phiau-chè) tòe-tio̍h?
Tī lán-ê chu-liāu lāi, ūi-sé ê chu-liāu sī kā pa̍t-ê ū bô-kâng ê tē-lí-iáⁿ hong-hiòng ê chu-liāu?
Tī lia̍t chhut ê chu-liāu-khò͘ tiong, ū nn̄g sió-chūn ê sī tī 2023 nî chhut-pán ê?
Tng-siaⁿ chiūⁿ chha-tiāu 'SEntFiN 1.0' chu-liāu-kè, siáⁿ chi̍t ê siāng sin ê chu-liāu sī choan-bô͘ teh hun-sek sin-bûn thâu-tiâu?
Tī chit ê lia̍t-toa̍t tang-tiong, ū siáng/siâng-kûn thàu-suí ê chu-liāu chòe chē?
Tōa-khuàn ê NLP jīm-bū, 'FiNER' ê tû-ê kah 'REFinD' ê tû-ê ūi-hē ē-tàng sím-mih phik-phêng?
answer: 'FiNER' sī siat-kè hō͘ chi̍t ê ki-pún ê NLP jīm-bū, Ming-chheng Tāi-chū Jīn-tī (NER), chē-sī kā siat-liāu chē-sī chāi-lâi ê tāi-chè, chē-sī khò-chè chāi-lâi ê kong-si. 'REFinD' thiau-chiàn chi̍t ê khah lūn-tiâu, āu-sū ê jīm-bū, siū-chāi kiám-tāi ê tāi-chè hō͘ kā tû-ê (chē-sī, jîn-lē-miâ-miâ, kong-sū-chîⁿ), Só͘-í, FiNER sī tiám-tiám tiāⁿ kiám-tāi ê 'chòe-chiá' lán-lâi REFinD sī tiám-tiám tiāⁿ kiám-tāi ê in 'hia̍h-tōaⁿ'.

question: Tùi siâu-su̍t lâi kóng, ū bô khòaⁿ-chāi ū tī 'thâu-ia̍h' (headlines) siâⁿ-thâu ê chū-liāu kap in chhut-pán nî-tāi ê sin-chè ū tiâu-kiāⁿ? Kái-soeh che ê lí-iû.
answer: Ū, chin chhin-chhin chū-chú. Saⁿ ê chū-liāu lóng ū chin-khó·-ài ê kóng-hoat 'thâu-ia̍h' tī in siâu-su̍t lāi-bīn (SEntFiN 1.0, Gold Commodity Dataset, kap MULTIFIN), lóng sī 2021 nî í-āu chhut-pán ê. Chá-kî chhut-pán ê chū-liāu, tī 2010 nî-tāi, bô kóng tio̍h chit ê te̍k-pia̍t ê tiâu-chú. Che sī kóng-bêng chòe-kīn ê chi̍t-kóa nî, chòe-kóa lâng khoàⁿ-chāi beh gián-kiù hâm-iú chin tiōng-iàu kap ū éng-hiáng-le̍k ê chāi-liāu thâu-ia̍h ê gí-giân.

question: Tī kim-iông bûn-chiá hun-sek tang-tiong, SentiWordNet kap SenticNet ê chú-iàu bo̍k-te̍k sī siáⁿ-mih?
answer: SentiWordNet kā sû-sè chha̍t sîn-sò͘ lâi thê-kiong chèng-bīn, hō͘-bīn, he̍k-chiá sī khó-kài-sèng ê sòng-chú; to̍h-sī SenticNet sī ha̍p-chè AI kap Semantic Web ki-su lâi kái-thé kap chòe sîn-chêng sū-bū tī kim-iông ê chiap-chhiok tang-tiong.
